episodes.title: Charles Manson - Ep 3. Spooks & Cults Part 2: The Process
episodes.description: Alright it's going off the deep end. We start delving into the Process Church of the Final Judgement. A very litigious cult who was in some capacity related to the Family. They started in England, moved to America and trafficked in a variety of weird shit. There's porn tapes, sacrifices, drugs, revenge and more.
subjects: Process Church of the Final Judgement
